  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Veritas Finance Private Limited</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Veritas is a lender providing financial access to micro and small businesses in semi-urban and rural areas in India. Being a big source of jobs, these businesses make up the backbone of the informal Indian economy. They are often family or individual run and find it difficult to access credit given their lack of formalisation and the absence of adequate documentation. Veritas provides these businesses with small loans for expansion and working capital, thereby also helping their financial inclusion and migration into the formal credit system. Our investment will help Veritas to grow and expand into Indian States, including the poorest states, such as Orissa</narrative>
  </description>
